data.description: Location! Location! A well maintained and located 2BR/2BA condo in Taos Ski Valley adjacent to central plaza area. Two Gas fireplaces. Ski locker with a short walk to the main lift. The Snakedance is close to the main lift, the central Plaza area and the Gondolita. Furnishings negotiable.       Condo is in rental program.  Restricted showing times.
